 *   - REFRESH_TOKEN_TTL    – refresh token lifetime (30 days)
 *   - MAX_FAILED_ATTEMPTS  – login attempt limit before account lock (5)
 *   - LOCK_DURATION_MS     – account lock duration (15 minutes)
 *
